PN,35101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FITV Border reporter Hannah Norbury's
OL,8,Finvestigation has revealed the ease,
OL,9,Fspeed and availability of synthetic
OL,10,Fopioids at the touch of a finger
OL,12,FA man says the ease and availability
OL,13,Fof drugs sold on apps, and which
OL,14,Fpromise to deliver to your door in as
OL,15,Flittle as one day, contributed to his
OL,16,Faddiction and cost him his family.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FEvery day we use our mobile phones;
OL,8,Fchecking social media apps, talking to
OL,9,Ffriends and family over messaging
OL,10,Fsites and checking our day-to-day
OL,11,Fnecessities like online banking.
OL,13,FThey have become a physical portal
OL,14,Fallowing us to find anything at the
OL,15,Ftouch of a finger.
OL,17,FAn ITV Border investigation has found
OL,18,Fthat now people are buying synthetic
OL,19,Fopioids through mobile phone apps,
OL,20,Fwhich claim to deliver within one to
OL,21,Fthree days.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FSynthetic opioids can be extremely
OL,8,Fdangerous and have been linked to some
OL,9,Fsuspected drug-related deaths in our
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,FStuart, whose name has been changed to
OL,13,Fprotect his identity, says the ease of
OL,14,Fbuying synthetic opioids through apps
OL,15,Fhelped to fuel his dangerous addiction
OL,16,Fand led him to losing his loved ones.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,F"It cost me my family, I lost them,"
OL,8,Fhe explained. "They (drugs) take over
OL,9,Fyour life, you don't have any time for
OL,10,Fanyone, even family. It hurts a lot
OL,11,Finside. But I've accepted what I've
OL,12,Fdone, and it was wrong.
OL,14,F"This is what it leads to - you lose
OL,15,Feveryone and you're oblivious in
OL,16,Faddiction, you're self-obsessed, self-
OL,17,Fcentred and you take, take, take."
OL,19,FStuart said he was in hospital with a
OL,20,Fhealth condition, and was prescribed
OL,21,Fstrong painkillers including morphine.
OL,26,@pD@UpmpD@[pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FThis was the start of addiction and
OL,8,Fled him to wanting more. He said he
OL,9,Fwent on the internet to find ways to
OL,10,Fbuy drugs, and within seconds found
OL,11,Fforums telling him which apps he could
OL,12,Fuse to do just that.
OL,14,FOne of the apps he said he purchased
OL,15,Fdrugs from was Telegram - an
OL,16,Fencrypted, instant messaging app, used
OL,17,Facross the world.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FStuart demonstrated how easily it was
OL,8,Fto purchase drugs from the app. No
OL,9,Fdark web, no cover-up. Drugs were
OL,10,Fbeing sold in front of our eyes.
OL,12,FWhat followed were pages full of
OL,13,Freviews about the speed of the
OL,14,Fdelivery and quality of the drugs.
OL,16,F"The internet opened a new Pandora's
OL,17,Fbox for more substances and it was
OL,18,Fthat easy," he said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,F"It was like typing into Google
OL,8,F'what's the weather like today?' but
OL,9,F'How do I get these drugs and where?""
OL,11,FAsked how quickly the drugs arrived,
OL,12,Fhe responded: "This is the madness
OL,13,Fbehind it. When you go to these places
OL,14,Fthey have options for delivery, so you
OL,15,Fhave 24 (hour) tracked, so it comes
OL,16,Fthe next day, if you order before 3pm
OL,17,FMonday to Friday."
OL,26,@wD@IpmwD@Npn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FStuart said the ease, speed, and
OL,8,Faccessibility of buying drugs online
OL,9,Fhad devastating consequences on his
OL,10,Fhealth, and at times caused him to
OL,11,Foverdose.
OL,13,F"Ambulances came out, and I was rushed
OL,14,Fto hospital," he said. "Did that fix
OL,15,Fme? No. (I) just got back and ordered
OL,16,Fmore.
OL,18,F"I could sit in hospital and order it
OL,19,Fand to me that's just mad, you don't
OL,20,Fhave to go to a shop, walk, you can
OL,21,Fjust order it by phone."
OL,26,@wD@IpmwD@Kpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FPages on the app claim that drugs
OL,8,Fbought online can be delivered within
OL,9,Fone to three days. We have seen no
OL,10,Fevidence of this but we contacted
OL,11,FRoyal Mail to confirm what regulations
OL,12,Fare in place to monitor illegal drugs
OL,13,Fin the postal system.
OL,15,FA Royal Mail spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fare legally obligated not to open
OL,17,Fpost. However, we will routinely
OL,18,Freport suspicious items to the
OL,19,Frelevant authorities for further
OL,20,Finspection.
OL,26,@wD@aOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,F"We also regularly assist police in
OL,8,Fthe course of their investigations and
OL,9,Fassist Border Force in their
OL,10,Fassessment of items that arrive from
OL,11,Fabroad."
OL,13,FWhat are synthetic opioids?
OL,15,FA national drug charity, With You, has
OL,16,Freported an increase in drugs being
OL,17,Fsold on apps.
OL,26,@sD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FJake Towns, from the organisation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We also see dealing through
OL,9,Fsecond hand clothing apps as well. So
OL,10,Fagain it comes with its own codes, so
OL,11,Fpeople can hide drugs within packages,
OL,12,Fwhich is a concern.
OL,14,F"It's also created a bit of a volatile
OL,15,Fmarket, in relation to substances that
OL,16,Fare available, and that includes
OL,17,Fpricing. With more saturation in the
OL,18,Fmarket, comes more competitive pricing
OL,19,Fwhich brings the price down but also
OL,20,Fadds more contaminants.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,F"We are seeing drugs mixed with
OL,8,Fdangerous substances like nitazines,
OL,9,Fwhich adds another layer of danger to
OL,10,Fpeople purchasing the substances."
OL,12,FHe added: "We're finding that people
OL,13,Fwho are wanting to abstain from a
OL,14,Fsubstance use are actually having
OL,15,Fdrugs promoted to them. And it's much
OL,16,Feasier access, so it's much easier to
OL,17,Fget hold of when people are trying to
OL,18,Fget away from that lifestyle."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FNot taking drugs would eliminate the
OL,8,Fpotential risk of overdose. But the
OL,9,Freality is far more complex.
OL,11,FCharities often focus on harm
OL,12,Freduction, and urge the public and
OL,13,Fthose using drugs to carry naloxone -
OL,14,Fa nasal spray that can reverse an
OL,15,Fopioid overdose.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FMr Towns added: "There are services
OL,8,Fthat will test drugs for you. Also
OL,9,Flook out for alerts which will make
OL,10,Fyou aware of the drugs that we find in
OL,11,Fthe area which are contaminated and
OL,12,Fposing a risk of overdose."
OL,14,FHow can you reduce harm?
OL,16,FWhat are the police doing about this
OL,17,Fissue?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FDave Allen, the Police, Fire and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner for Cumbria has had a
OL,9,Flong, varied career, working in
OL,10,Fvarious teams tackling drug activity,
OL,11,Fincluding at the National Crime Agency.
OL,13,FWhen I showed him our evidence of how
OL,14,Feasy it was to buy drugs on apps, his
OL,15,Ffirst response was: "It doesn't
OL,16,Fsurprise me."
OL,18,FHe added: "It's just like a normal
OL,19,Fpurchasing website, you go on an app
OL,20,Fand click what you want, really it is
OL,21,Fexactly the same.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,F"There's been drugs bought through
OL,8,Ffast parcels for years. There is more
OL,9,Fof it now and a growing trend for it.
OL,11,F"The police, border force, curriers,
OL,12,Fare aware of this happening. They have
OL,13,Fa good success rate, but will they
OL,14,Fstop all of it? No.
OL,16,F"They are very good business people,
OL,17,Fthey will adapt whatever works."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FSocial media platforms have faced
OL,8,Fpressure to moderate illegal content
OL,9,Funder the Online Safety Act. But
OL,10,FStuart told me that in his experience,
OL,11,Fnew channels would often emerge to
OL,12,Freplace those that are shut down.
OL,14,FThe police acknowledge that end-to-end
OL,15,Fencrypted apps make it harder to catch
OL,16,Fcriminals, but say that it is not
OL,17,Fimpossible.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FMr Allen continued: "What I would say
OL,8,Fis everything digital leaves a
OL,9,Ffootprint and a trace, and at some
OL,10,Fpoint it will lead back to the dealer,
OL,11,Fand that's how the police will find
OL,12,Fyou."
OL,14,FWhen questioned about what more the
OL,15,Fgovernment should be doing, he said:
OL,16,F"Certainly it is like anything to do
OL,17,Fwith social media, there probably does
OL,18,Fneed to be greater regulation around
OL,19,Fwhat's done.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G18/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,F"Certainly if you're offering drugs
OL,8,Ffor sale online that are unlawful,
OL,9,Fthere has got to be better ways of
OL,10,Fgetting and accessing that information.
OL,12,F"It can be quite difficult, especially
OL,13,Fif the service provider for that
OL,14,Finternet set up is abroad, that needs
OL,15,Fto be quicker, there needs to be
OL,16,Fbetter ways of getting that
OL,17,Finformation."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G19/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FIn response to the ITV investigation,
OL,8,Fa Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,9,Fare not complacent about the threat of
OL,10,Fsynthetic opioids and are determined
OL,11,Fto prevent these highly dangerous
OL,12,Fsubstances from reaching our
OL,13,Fcommunities.
OL,15,F"We will continue our engagement with
OL,16,Fpartners across health, policing,
OL,17,Fwider public services and online
OL,18,Fplatforms to drive down drug misuse,
OL,19,Fprevent deaths and move forward with
OL,20,Four mission to make streets safer."
OL,26,@pD@aOUwD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G20/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35121
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776867068
OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FThe Home Office added: "Synthetic
OL,8,Fopioids pose a serious and evolving
OL,9,Fthreat and the government is
OL,10,Fresponding with urgency.
OL,12,F"The crossgovernment Synthetic
OL,13,FOpioids Taskforce brings departments
OL,14,Ftogether to coordinate and strengthen
OL,15,Fthe UK's response to emerging risks."
OL,17,FIn October 2025, the Department for
OL,18,FHealth and Social care launched a
OL,19,Fpublic awareness campaign focused on
OL,20,Fthe dangers of new patterns of drug
OL,21,Fuse.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G21/24
