OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FThe government says these measures
OL,8,F"build on our ongoing efforts to
OL,9,Freduce the supply of synthetic
OL,10,Fopioids, including the recent ban of
OL,11,F22 additional synthetic drugs to
OL,12,Fprevent gangs from evading UK drug
OL,13,Flaws".
OL,15,FIt also added that the Online Safety
OL,16,FAct applies to all platforms,
OL,17,Fregardless of size or scale.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G22/24
