OL,3,CFrom app to door in 24 hours: How the
OL,4,Conline drug market is fuelling
OL,5,Caddiction
OL,7,FA spokesperson from Telegram said:
OL,8,F"The sale of illicit substances is
OL,9,Fexplicitly forbidden by Telegram's
OL,10,Fterms of service and such content is
OL,11,Fremoved whenever discovered.
OL,13,F"Moderators empowered with custom AI
OL,14,Ftools proactively monitor public parts
OL,15,Fof the platform and accept reports in
OL,16,Forder to remove millions of pieces of
OL,17,Fharmful content each day, including
OL,18,Fthe sale of drugs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G23/24
